node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Caduceus Cellars on July 27, 2021. May be an image of bottle.

node.text: Caduceus Cellars 2017 Nagual de la NAGA. First produced in 2004, this year’s Arizona NAGA blend is 90% Sangiovese, 5% Souzao, 5% Negroamaro.  This is the third vintage of NAGA from our largest Northern AZ site, Eliphante. It’s the first vintage to include Negroamaro. Get your bottle online, in our Jerome tasting room, or at @merkinvineyards Old Town Scottsdale. Please note: online orders will ship as temperatures allow. #arizonawine #negroamaro #sangiovese #caduceuscellars #jeromeaz

node.text: Peter Parker has been hangin around while we’re prepping the press and de-Stemmer for Vintage 2021. @puscifer @caduceuscellars @merkinvineyards @four8wineworks

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Caduceus Cellars on July 19, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
Caduceus Cellars 2016 Nagual del MARZO. This is fruit from our Marzo block in Yavapai County, AZ. A blend of 50% Sangiovese, 50% Cabernet Sauvignon. A subtle, elegant, restrained wine with just a kiss of oak from its 20 months in large Botte/Casks. Of all of our wines, the MARZO has led the way in showcasing our submerged cap and extended maceration approach in the cellar. Fantastic old-world results. 6 bottle limit per customer. Available online, in our Jerome tasting room, and at @merkinvineyards Old Town Scottsdale. Please note, online orders will ship as temperatures allow.
#arizonawine #caduceuscellars  #sangiovese #cabernetsauvignon

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Caduceus Cellars in Jerome, Arizona with @texsomiwa. May be an image of bottle.

node.text:
We are pleased to announce that 2018 Nagual del SENSEI has been awarded a GOLD medal in the 2021 Texsom IWA. This is 60% Sagrantino / 40% Souzao, from the Eliphante Block. Although tiers I & II of the Velvet Slippers Club have already received a sneak peek in their latest shipment, SENSEI will not be officially released until October 29. Mark your calendars. Limited quantities.

@texsomiwa
#sagrantino
#souzao #arizonawine

node.text:
New release alert: Available Friday (5/28), Caduceus Cellars 2018 AIRAVATA and 2016 SANCHA. Also, we are digging into the archives to release two new box sets. A 3-bottle box from the 2009 vintage and a 6-bottle box featuring early Velvet Slippers Club (VSC) selections with a 2011 Nagual del JUDITH. Get yours at the Caduceus Tasting Room in Jerome, online at www.caduceus.org, and at @merkinvineyards Old Town Scottsdale.

*Please note: Due to high temperatures in Arizona, the archive boxes will not be available in our online store until the fall.
#arizonawine #caduceuscellars #velvetslippersclub
